name: Immersive Horizon
summary: Discover the world like never before with IMMERSIVE HORIZON by XR Horizon! Our app brings immersive 360-degree videos of natural wonders, historic sites, and more right to your fingertips. As a leader in AR, VR, MR, and AI, XR Horizon delivers fully interactive, panoramic views perfect for education, exploration, and entertainment. Dive into a new dimension of discovery with IMMERSIVE HORIZON—your gateway to a world of endless virtual adventures!
